summary: I am a cultural and touristic professional entertainer with international experience. I am currently looking for new challenges in the entertainement field in the Netherlands. I am a dancer, a theater comedian and I enjoy introducing events. I am creative. I speak several languages including english, french, turkish, russian, german and arabic which gives me the possibility to work in mutlicultural and international organisations.
